K12D0447_H0419:187a-17: rnal 'byor chen po bas las kyi rgyal po mchog
K12D0447_H0419:187a-18: gi ting nge 'dzin la brten nas sems can gyi
K12D0447_H0419:187a-19: don ji ltar rab tu spyod par bgyid /

K12D0447_H0419:187a-21: ji srid du zhi ba la sogs pa'i las kyis
K12D0447_H0419:187a-22: sems can gyi don mi byed pa de srid du
K12D0447_H0419:187a-23: yang dag pa'i mtha' la rab tu gnas par 'gyur
K12D0447_H0419:187a-24: ro // gang du sems can gyi don bya bar

K12D0447_H0419:187a-26: pas yang dag pa'i mtha' las langs te sems can
K12D0447_H0419:187a-27: gyi don byas nas yang dag pa'i mtha' nyid du
K12D0447_H0419:187a-29: de nas byams pa la sogs pa byang chub sems
K12D0447_H0419:187a-30: dpa' chen po rnams dga' zhing mgu la yid rangs
K12D0447_H0419:187a-31: te dga' ba dang yid bde ba skyes nas cang
K12D0447_H0419:187a-33: ye shes rdo rje kun las btus pa zhes bya ba rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud las /
K12D0447_H0419:187a-34: bde ba chen po'i le'u ste rim par phye ba gnyis pa'o //
K12D0447_H0419:187b-0: rgya gar gyi mkhan po dzny'a na ka ra'i zhal snga @187b nas dang /
K12D0447_H0419:187b-1: zhu chen gyi lo ts'a pa khu ston dngos grub kyis bsgyur /
K12D0447_H0419:187b-2: slad nas bla ma de nyid dang /
K12D0447_H0419:187b-3: dge slong tshul khrims rgyal bas zhus shing gtan la phab pa /
K12D0447_H0419:187b-4: ye shes rdo rje kun las btus //
K12D0447_H0419:187b-5: rnal 'byor chen po'i gsal byed yin //
K12D0447_H0419:187b-6: ye shes rang bzhin 'khor ba dang //
K12D0447_H0419:187b-7: mya ngan 'das pa'i ngo bo la //
